subsection.p:
So near P,
\boxed{ F(2+\Delta x,1+\Delta y) \approx F(2,1) + \left( \frac65\Delta x+\frac25\Delta y,\; \frac25\Delta x+\Delta y \right). }
The linear machine acting on the small displacement is
(\Delta x,\Delta y) \longmapsto \left( \frac65\Delta x+\frac25\Delta y,\; \frac25\Delta x+\Delta y \right).
As a matrix, this is
\boxed{ \begin{pmatrix} \frac65 \amp \frac25\\[1mm] \frac25 \amp 1 \end{pmatrix} \begin{pmatrix} \Delta x\\ \Delta y \end{pmatrix}. }

